Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: medialog.tinymceplugins.placegallery
Version: 0.0.2alpha
Summary: An not so advanced TinyMCE plugin for handling links to galleries
Home-page: http://svn.plone.org/svn/collective/medialog.tinymceplugins.placegallery/
Author: Espen Moe-Nilssen
Author-email: espen@medialog.no
License: GPL
Description: Introduction
        ============
        
        This is a plugin for `TinyMCE`__ editor for Plone.
        __ http://plone.org/products/tinymce/
        
        It is trying to add a "place gallerybutton" for collective.plonetruegallery and collective.gallery
        You must whitelist "iframe' in safe-html
        You must also enable "background" and "overflow" id you want to use those options
        
        Changelog
        =========
        
        0.0.1 alpha
        --------
        
        * Initialversion
        
        0.0.2 alpha
        --------
        
        * Added a few options, like setting width and height of gallery.
        
        
